reviewText: My son first saw this when he was nine ( there is a lot of drinking in it, just FYI), but the skateboarding was incredible.  He is now 19, and found it again on Amazon, and bought it.  This was the DVD that really influenced his style of skateboarding.  Iconic skate video, a must see if you are interested in or just love skateboarding.
I like the video. I loved seeing andrew reynolds part in Baker 3. Why are the above prices so much?

This is a really good skatevideo made by one of the most respected skate compaines of all time Baker. All the parts in here are insane!!Especially Dustin Dollin's part and Jim Greco's. The only reason i don't give this 5 stars is because of the cussing so if your family is against swearing and beer drinking watch out! But if your friends and family are okay with that go for it it's worth every penny!
